        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Comparison of Tigridiopalma exalata and T. magnifica: A-E Tigridiopalma exalata a-e T. magnifica A, a flowering plants B, b leaf bases, abaxial view C, c flowers, front view D, d stamens, side view E, e infructescences, side view. Photographed by Si-Jin Zeng." , "Figure 3. Tigridiopalma exalata S. Jin Zeng, Y. C. Xu & D. F. Cui: A plant B leaf base, abaxial view C opening flower, front view D petal, front view E longer stamens, side view F longer stamen, front view G short stamens, side view H short stamen, front view I opening flower, longitudinal section J hypanthium, with attached style, longitudinal section. Scale bars: 5 mm. Drawn by Ding-Han Cui." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531680" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/531679" .

